T = \\left( \\begin{array}{cccc}
1 & 0 & 0 & translation_x \\\\ 
0 & 1 & 0 & translation_y \\\\ 
0 & 0 & 1 & translation_z \\\\ 
0 & 0 & 0 & 1 \\\\ 
\\end{array} \\right),
$$
.RE
